e foods that help prevent obesity heart disease and cancer subscribe to our mailing list for the latest news and offers click here to join lemons  limoneiralemons with  acres of lemons throughout california limoneira is one of the largest lemon producers in north america in its  years of operation the company has introduced a number of innovations that have added significantly to the industry such as improved storage methods and sophisticated harvest practices and equipment in the ’s limoneira developed the limco a bred in limoneira’s olivelands a orchard a new lemon variety that proved more resistant to disease yielded more fruit was high in quality and maintained a strong shelf life this variety remains one of the standard bearers for lemon production throughout the world today limoneira maintains a demonstration orchard of over  citrus varieties on limoneira ranch property in santa paula to satisfy consumer tastes and to help keep the company at the cutting edge of new citrus products research continues to be vital we partner with the university of california’s agriculture and natural resources program to further agriculture’s forward momentum and we work with leading partners in our northern and southern farming operations to grow harvest and pack efficiently and sustainability sometimes the old ways are the best ways limoneira’s mediterranean style packing house built in the ’s received recognition for its classic design from the southern california chapter of the american institute of architects in the early twentieth century after all these years it still operates at peak performance with our vertical integration from tree to plate we are able to achieve efficiencies through all parts of the distribution chain resulting in the highest quality and service possible for our customers our global marketing connections and harvesting packing and quality control capabilities ensure that the customer in tokyo enjoying our lemons in a delicious fish recipe will be as happy as our north american customer enjoying a refreshing glass of lemonade made with quality limoneira lemons agribusiness lemons customers vertical integration global network brands lemon specifications food safety quality customer service sustainability shopper health heritage food safety sustainability lifestyle beauty cleaning packing innovations community limoneira kids recipes lemon facts availability one world of fresh citrus interested in carrying our lemons testimonials avocados oranges specialties ranches availability subscribe to our mailing list for the latest news and offers click here to join about us  limoneiraabout us the limoneira company was founded in ventura county california in  its founders were pioneers of spirit and vision that helped lay the foundations of a thriving california citrus industry their dedication and innovation in the agricultural industry helped found and develop many institutions that still exist sunkist growers fruit growers supply and diamond walnut today limoneira has evolved into a global company whose mission is to preserve and promote its tradition heritage and legacy in agriculture community development and stewardship to maximize value for its shareholders with nearly  acres of agricultural production limoneira is one of the largest providers of lemons and avocados in the united states in addition to agricultural investments limoneira has a long history of community building and new livewalkwork neighborhoods are close to shovel ready commercial and residential income producing and forsale properties round out our portfolio finally investments that integrate directly with our agriculture and real estate business relate to stewardship sustainability has been woven into the company’s fabric for over a century strategic investments in water solar soil and ipm integrated pest management enable us to do well by doing good we also believe that true sustainability means taking care of the communities in which we operate and taking care of our employees these are investments that we are truly happy to make about us mission statement community history subscribe to our mailing list for the latest news and offers click here to join limoneira people  limoneiralimoneira people senior management   harold edwards presidentceo   x hedwardslimoneiracom alex teague senior vice president   x amteaguelimoneiracom  joseph d rumley chief financial officer   x  jrumleylimoneiracom sales   john carter director of global sales   x jcarterlimoneiracom susan ng director of international business development   x snglimoneiracom dan bissett associate director – global sales   x dbissettlimoneiracom john caragliano eastern sales director   jcaraglianolimoneiracom rick goodside domestic sales manager lemon operations   x rgoodsidelimoneiracom stephen sheldon business development manager lemon operations   x ssheldonlimoneiracom maria vargas sales coordinator   x mvargaslimoneiracom jocelyn hernandez sales assistant   x jhernandezlimoneiracom farming and harvest   mark palamountain senior director agricultural operations   x marklimoneiracom dan galbraith director of farming – northern ranches   x dgalbraithlimoneiracom gus gunderson director of farming – southern ranches   x ggundersonlimoneiracom vince giacolone director of desert farming operations   vgiacolonelimoneiracom stewart lockwood director for field operations   x slockwoodlimoneiracom admin   don delmatoff director of compliance  special projects   x ddelmatofflimoneiracom eric tovias director of information systems   x etoviaslimoneiracom greg hamm vice president controller   x ghammlimoneiracom john chamberlain director of marketing   x jchamberlainlimoneiracom kathleen thompson director of human resources   x kthompsonlimoneiracom rosie castillo property manager   x rcastillolimoneiracom anthony ecuyer director of packing lemon operations   aecuyerlimoneiracom ryan nasalroad manager service operations   x rnasalroadlimoneiracom   corporate ne